sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User Workstation<br/>(kubectl rhaii-validate all)
    participant K8s as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Controller as Controller<br/>(same binary, CLI mode)
    participant GPUJob as GPU Check Job Pod<br/>(per-node, privileged)
    participant Host as Host Filesystem<br/>(/host chroot)
    participant RDMAJob as RDMA Node Check Job<br/>(per-node, privileged)
    participant IperfServer as iperf3 Server Pod<br/>5201/TCP
    participant IperfClient as iperf3 Client Pod
    participant TCPServer as TCP Latency Server<br/>12865/TCP
    participant TCPClient as TCP Latency Client
    participant PingServer as ibv_rc_pingpong Server<br/>18515+N/TCP
    participant PingClient as ibv_rc_pingpong Client
    participant BWServer as ib_write_bw Server<br/>18515/TCP GPUDirect
    participant BWClient as ib_write_bw Client
    participant CM as ConfigMap<br/>(JSON Report)

    Note over User,CM: Phase 1: Setup & API Checks (Tier 1)
    User->>K8s: kubectl rhaii-validate all<br/>Auth: kubeconfig Bearer Token
    K8s->>Controller: Start validation
    Controller->>K8s: Create Namespace + RBAC<br/>rhaii-validation namespace
    Controller->>K8s: List nodes (detect platform)<br/>Scan all nodes for labels
    Controller->>K8s: Create ConfigMap (platform config)
    Controller->>K8s: Check CRDs (Gateway API,<br/>InferencePool, LeaderWorkerSet,<br/>cert-manager)
    Controller->>K8s: Check operator health<br/>(cert-manager, Istio, LWS)

    Note over User,CM: Phase 2: Per-Node GPU Checks (Tier 2)
    Controller->>K8s: Deploy per-node GPU check Jobs
    K8s->>GPUJob: Schedule privileged Job pods
    GPUJob->>Host: chroot /host<br/>nvidia-smi / rocm-smi
    Host-->>GPUJob: GPU driver status, ECC errors,<br/>PCIe topology, NUMA mapping
    GPUJob-->>K8s: JSON report (pod logs)
    K8s-->>Controller: Collect reports from pod logs

    Note over User,CM: Phase 3: Per-Node RDMA Checks (Tier 2)
    Controller->>K8s: Deploy per-node RDMA check Jobs
    K8s->>RDMAJob: Schedule privileged Job pods
    RDMAJob->>Host: chroot /host<br/>ibv_devices, ibstat, sysfs
    Host-->>RDMAJob: RDMA devices, NIC status,<br/>GPU-NIC-NUMA topology
    RDMAJob-->>K8s: JSON report (pod logs)
    K8s-->>Controller: Collect reports

    Note over User,CM: Phase 4: Multi-Node Network Tests
    Controller->>K8s: Deploy iperf3 server + client Jobs
    K8s->>IperfServer: Start iperf3 -s
    K8s->>IperfClient: Start iperf3 -c
    IperfClient->>IperfServer: TCP bandwidth test<br/>5201/TCP, no encryption
    IperfServer-->>IperfClient: Bandwidth results

    Controller->>K8s: Deploy TCP latency server + client Jobs
    K8s->>TCPServer: Start tcp-lat-server
    K8s->>TCPClient: Start tcp-lat-client
    TCPClient->>TCPServer: TCP echo round-trip<br/>12865/TCP, no encryption
    TCPServer-->>TCPClient: Latency measurements

    Note over User,CM: Phase 5: RDMA Connectivity & Bandwidth
    Controller->>K8s: Deploy ibv_rc_pingpong Jobs (mesh)
    K8s->>PingServer: Start pingpong server
    K8s->>PingClient: Start pingpong client
    PingClient->>PingServer: RDMA connectivity test<br/>18515+N/TCP per NIC pair
    PingServer-->>PingClient: Connectivity results

    Controller->>K8s: Deploy ib_write_bw Jobs
    K8s->>BWServer: Start ib_write_bw server
    K8s->>BWClient: Start ib_write_bw client
    BWClient->>BWServer: RDMA bandwidth test<br/>18515/TCP GPUDirect CUDA
    BWServer-->>BWClient: Bandwidth results

    Note over User,CM: Phase 6: Report & Cleanup
    Controller->>K8s: Store JSON report in ConfigMap
    K8s->>CM: Persist results
    Controller->>K8s: Clean up Jobs + RBAC
    Controller-->>User: Display results<br/>(table or JSON output)
